.nlm.nih.gov) and TOXMAP (http://toxmap.nlm.nih.gov)\r\n\r\n\r\n',1245079133,1247851842,'tox',0,1247851842,0,0),(52,'Eighteenth Century Collections Online',1,'1701-1800',24,'http://infotrac.galegroup.com/itweb/morg77564?db=ECCO','','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask A Librarian','http://www.libraries.wvu.edu/ask/','138,000 English-language titles and editions published between 1701 and 1800, digitized and fully searchable. ECCO includes every significant English-language and foreign-language title printed in the United Kingdom, along with thousands of important works from the Americas. \r\n',1245079133,1278457931,'1197579928',0,1278457931,0,0),(53,'Abstracts in Anthropology',1,'2000-',17,'http://anthropology.metapress.com/(pqmabrfhc1lvxi55jmgkp045)/app/home/search-abstracts.asp','','NULL',2,0,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://www.libraries.wvu.edu/ask','Abstracts for articles in several hundred anthropology periodicals, covering a broad spectrum of significant current topics.  Please remember to logout.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',1245079133,1245929120,'1142440570',0,1245929120,0,0),(54,'Worldwide Political Science Abstracts',1,'1975-',41,'http://search.proquest.com/wpsa?accountid=2837','','11',2,0,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://westvirginia.libanswers.com/','The database provides citations, abstracts, and indexing of the international serials literature in political science and its complementary fields, including international relations, law, and public administration / policy.  Use Find it @ WVU to connect to full text articles.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',1245079133,1294944542,'1124978688',0,1294894800,0,0),(55,'Household Products Health &amp; Safety Information',1,'Information is extracted from the Consumer Product',14,'http://householdproducts.nlm.nih.gov','','5',3,0,0,0,30,'Household Product Database Help Topics\r\n\r\nFrequently Asked Questions','http://householdproducts.nlm.nih.gov/help.htm\r\n\r\nhttp://householdproducts.nlm.nih.gov/faq.htm','This database links over 8,000 consumer bra