79133,1382629251,'1120765289',1,1382629251,0,0),(177,'Science Citation Index Expanded',1,'1986-',22,'http://isiknowledge.com/?DestApp=WOS&editions=SCI','','6',2,0,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian\r\nSlides with audio','http://westvirginia.libanswers.com/\r\nhttp://isiwebofknowledge.com/training_support/training/recordedtraining/#wos','Science Citation Index Expanded, a part of the Web of Science is made available with funding from the WVU Research Corp.  It provides access to current and retrospective multidisciplinary information from high impact research journals in the world.  It also provides a unique search method, cited reference searching. With it, users can navigate forward, backward, and through the literature, searching all disciplines and time spans to uncover all the information relevant to their research.\r\n\r\n\r\n',1245079133,1266852460,'1134498063',0,1266814800,0,0),(178,'JSTOR',1,'Varies by title.  See title lists in the collectio',0,'http://www.jstor.org','','3',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://www.libraries.wvu.edu/ask','JSTOR is an archive of more than 1,000 scholarly, interdisciplinary journals, with full coverage for all but the most current 3-5 years.  The entire archive is full-text searchable, offers search term highlighting, includes high-quality images, and is interlinked by millions of citations and references.\r\n',1245079133,1419032402,'jstor',0,1419032402,0,0),(179,'MountainLynx',1,'',0,'http://mountainlynx.lib.wvu.edu/','','2',3,0,0,0,30,'','','WVU Libraries online catalog; use it to find   books, periodicals, microforms, and media materials owned by the libraries.  It contains holdings for all the WVU Libraries including Downtown Campus, Evansdale Library, Law Library, Health Sciences Library, and Charleston Division Library.\r\n\r\n\r\n',1245079133,1328631627,'mtnlynxcat',0,1328631627,0,0),(180,'Tests in Print (now included in Mental Measurements Yearbook)',1,'',32,'http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=ip,uid&profile=ehost&de