om','','3',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://www.libraries.wvu.edu/ask/','CivilENGINEERINGnetBASE is a collection of handbooks that are full-text searchable. Categories covered in CivilENGINEERINGnetBASE (but not limited to) include:\r\n\r\n    * Civil Engineering\r\n    * Computer Engineering\r\n    * Industrial Engineering &amp;amp; Manufacturing\r\n    * Mechanical Engineering \r\n\r\n',1245079133,1246279084,'1223299246',0,1246279084,0,0),(221,'Dissertation Abstracts (Now Proquest Dissertations and Theses)',1,'1861 - present',41,'http://search.proquest.com/pqdtft?accountid=2837','','11',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://www.libraries.wvu.edu/ask','',1245079133,1347632483,'diss',0,1347632483,0,0),(325,'Springer eBooks',1,'1997-',66,'http://link.springer.com/search?facet-content-type=%22Book%22','','3',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://www.libraries.wvu.edu/ask/','Springer eBooks includes more than 23,000 eBook titles, divided into twelve subject collections: behavioral science; computer science; biomedical and life sciences; engineering; medicine; mathematics and statistics; humanities, social sciences and law; physics and astronomy; business and economics; earth and environmental science; chemistry and materials science; professional and applied computing; and architecture and design.\r\n',1296589820,1419032542,'1296589820',0,1419032542,0,0),(222,'Complete Dictionary of Scientific Biography',1,'',24,'http://go.galegroup.com/ps/infomark.do?eisbn=9780684315591&userGroupName=morg77564&prodId=GVRL&action=interpret&type=aboutBook&version=1.0','','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask A Librarian','http://www.libraries.wvu.edu/ask/','Provides information on the history of science through articles on the professional lives of scientists. All periods of science from classical antiquity to modern times are represented.\r\n',1245079133,1421357889,'1200506353',0,1421357889,0,0),(223,'BIOSIS Previews',1,'1926-present',0,'http://apps.webofknowledge.com/BIOSIS_GeneralSearch_input.do?