iple publishers.  The 1,600 e-books are divided into medicine, nursing, and allied health and may be searched or browsed. ',1268767092,1273846886,'1268767092',0,1277438400,0,0),(299,'CREDO Reference',1,'',0,'http://www.credoreference.com','http://www.credoreference.com','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://www.libraries.wvu.edu/ask','A collection of nearly 500 encyclopedias, dictionaries, and other reference books provides a good starting point for research.',1269033404,1354546892,'1269033404',1,1354546892,0,0),(302,'Global Health',2,'1973 - present',32,'http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=uid&user=wvu&password=hsl','http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=uid&user=wvu&password=hsl','NULL',3,0,0,1,48,'See HELP link at the upper right of the main screen in the database.','','Global Health is a public health database with more than 1.4 million records. It contains information from over 3,500 serials, books, book chapters, conference proceedings, patents, theses and electronic only publications from more than 150 countries. \r\n\r\nSubject coverage includes international health, biomedical life sciences, non-communicable diseases, public health nutrition, food safety and hygiene, occupational health, toxicology, health services, and maternal/child health. \r\n',1270738893,1270741052,'1270738893',0,1273204800,0,0),(303,'Health Policy Reference Center',2,'',32,'http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=uid&user=wvu&password=hsl','http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=uid&user=wvu&password=hsl','NULL',3,1,0,1,48,'See HELP link at the upper right of the main screen of the database.','','The Health Policy Reference Center is designed to support the informational needs of corporations, medical institutions, government agencies, and other entities relative to health policy. This collection offers full-text coverage from more than 200 titles of information relevant to many areas integral to health policy including, but not limited to: