ian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Passport is a global market research database providing statistics, analysis, reports, surveys and breaking news on industries, markets, products, countries, and consumers worldwide.',1405449379,1426171917,'1405449379',0,1426171917,0,0),(474,'ProQuest Historical Newspapers-Black Newspapers',1,'1893-2005',41,'http://search.proquest.com/?accountid=2837&selectids=1005880,1007272,1005676,1005879,1005877,1005671,1005670,1005878,1005672','','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','ProQuest Historical Newspapers-Black Newspapers includes 9 newspapers and offers primary source material for the study of American history and African-American culture, history, politics, and the arts.\r\n\r\nNewspapers included are: Chicago Defender, The Baltimore Afro-American, New York Amsterdam News, Pittsburgh Courier, Los Angeles Sentinel, Atlanta Daily World, The Norfolk Journal and Guide, The Philadelphia Tribune, and Cleveland Call and Post. ',1408035988,1408037901,'1408035988',0,1408037901,0,0),(475,'Proquest History Vault: Slavery and the Law',1,'',41,'http://search.proquest.com/historyvault ','','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Archival material related to race, slavery, and free Blacks petitions to southern legislatures and southern courts. The collection includes:\r\n\r\nSeries I: Petitions to State Legislatures offers access to important but virtually unused primary source materials that were scattered in state archives of Alabama, Delaware, Florida, Mississippi, Missouri,North Carolina, South Carolina, Tennessee, Texas, and Virginia. The collection includes virtually all extant legislative petitions on the subject of race and slavery.\r\n\r\nSeries II: Petitions to Southern County Courts were collected from local courthouses,and candidly document the realities of slavery at the most immediate grassroots level in southern society. It was at county courthouses where the vast majority of disputes over the institution of slavery were referred. The petitions that were filed provide some of the most revealing documentation in existence on the functioning of the slave system.\r\n\r\nSlavery and the Law also includes State Slavery Statutes, a master record of the laws governing American slavery, covering 1789&ndash;1865. ',1408549406,1408549656,'1408549406',0,1408549656,0,0),(479,'Gender Studies Database',1,'1972-',32,'http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=ip,uid&profile=ehost&defaultdb=fmh','','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Gender Studies Database combines Women&rsquo;s Studies International and Men&rsquo;s Studies databases with the coverage of sexual diversity issues and the full spectrum of gender-engaged scholarship inside and outside academia. Several thousand links to freely available and indexed full-text articles and documents on the Internet are available. Source documents include professional journals, conference papers, books, book chapters, government reports, discussion and working papers, theses &amp; dissertations and other sources. Several hundred links provide access to carefully selected and important websites. This database includes more than 921,000 records with coverage spanning from 1972 and earlier to the presen',1408993725,1408993725,'1408993725',0,1408993725,0,0),(480,'Applied Science and Technology Source',1,'',32,'http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=ip,uid&profile=ehost&defaultdb=aci','','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Applied Science &amp; Technology Source offers extensive coverage of research and development within a wide variety of applied science and computing disciplines, including aeronautics, nuclear engineering, and neural networks. The database offers full text for almost 1,200 journals, citations to millions of articles.',1408994253,1408994253,'1408994253',0,1408994253,0,0),(481,'American Indian Histories and Cultures',1,'',0,'http://www.aihc.amdigital.co.uk/','','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian\r\nTake a tour to learn more','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/\r\nhttp://www.aihc.amdigital.co.uk/Introduction/TakeATour','American Indian Histories and Cultures features a wide range of materials including:Manuscripts (treaties, speeches, petitions, diaries, travel journals, ledger books, Artwork (illustrations, sketches, watercolours, oil paintings, American Indian art), American Indian Newspapers covering the 1960s to 1990s, Rare Printed Books,Photographs,and Maps.\r\n\r\nScope of the Collection:\r\n\r\nAllowing for the study of American Indian history from the early colonial period to the civil rights movement of the twentieth century,American Indian Histories and Cultures provides a rich variety of material from the Edward E. Ayer Collection at the Newberry Library. The project covers topics such as early encounters between American Indians and Europeans; American Indians and the colonial powers, and later, the US government; the indigenous peoples of Mexico; conflict, wars and military contact; the fur trade and Indian traders; education and American Indian boarding schools, and the civil rights movement and political activism.',1408994830,1426172201,'1408994830',0,1426172201,0,0),(482,'Met Opera on Demand: Student Access',1,'',0,'http://metopera.org/ondemand/index.aspx ','http://metopera.org/ondemand/index.aspx ','3',2,1,0,0,28,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Met Opera on Demand delivers access to more than 500 Met performances, including more than 70 past performances from the Met&rsquo;s Live in HD series, as well as more than 350 classic full-length video and audio performances. ',1410801681,1432214958,'1410801681',0,1432214958,0,0),(483,'Naxos Video Library',1,'',0,'http://WVUWL.NaxosVideoLibrary.com ','http://WVUWL.NaxosVideoLibrary.com ','3',2,0,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Naxos brings you a streaming video library of classical music performances, opera, ballet, live concerts and documentaries. Watch the world&#039;s greatest opera houses, ballet companies, orchestras and artists perform on demand!',1410808072,1432134380,'1410808072',0,1432134380,0,0),(484,'American Song',2,'',7,' http://search.alexanderstreet.com/amso',' http://search.alexanderstreet.com/amso','3',2,1,0,1,48,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','American Song is a streaming audio collection of American roots music and pre-1960 American popular music, providing streaming access to over half a million tracks.',1410881164,1410881300,'1410881164',0,1416114000,0,0),(485,'Opera in Video ',1,'',7,'http://search.alexanderstreet.com/opiv','http://search.alexanderstreet.com/opiv','3',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Opera in Video is a collection of operatic performances covering the most commonly studied operas in music history, opera literature, and performance classes. The collection contains 500 hours of video comprising 288 operatic works.',1410881481,1414765947,'1410881481',0,0,0,0),(486,'Smithsonian Global Sound for Libraries',1,'',7,'http://search.alexanderstreet.com/glmu','http://search.alexanderstreet.com/glmu','3',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Smithsonian Global Sound for Libraries is a streaming audio collection of world music. It currently provides streaming access to over 42,000 tracks from the Smithsonian archives and world music archives in Asia and Africa, and is growing regularly as new recordings are added.  ',1410890319,1427914147,'1410890319',0,1427914147,0,0),(487,'Entertainment Industry Magazine Archive',1,'',41,'http://search.proquest.com/eima?accountid=2837','https://trials.proquest.com/trials/trialSummary.action?view=subject&trialBean.token=0JJIKWOZVJ9HLAFXDM0I','3',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','An archival research resource containing primary sources for studying the history of the film and entertainment industries, from the era of vaudeville and silent movies through to 2000. The core US and UK trade magazines covering film, music, broadcasting and theater are all included, together with film fan magazines and music press titles. Magazines have been scanned cover-to-cover in high-resolution color, with granular indexing of all articles, covers, ads and reviews.',1410971702,1425410060,'1410971702',0,1425410060,0,0),(488,'Women&#039;s Wear Daily Archive',1,'1910-present',41,'http://search.proquest.com/wwd/arts/fromDatabasesLayer?accountid=2837','http://search.proquest.com/wwd/arts/fromDatabasesLayer?accountid=2837','3',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','A comprehensive archive of Women&rsquo;s Wear Daily, from the first issue in 1910 to material from within the last twelve months, reproduced in high-resolution images. Every page, article, advertisement and cover has been included, with searchable text and indexing. The Women&rsquo;s Wear Daily Archive preserves one of the fashion industry&#039;s most influential reads. Key moments in the history of the industry, as well as major designers, brands, retailers and advertisers are all covered in this publication of record.',1410972448,1425399304,'1410972448',0,1425399304,0,0),(490,'International Index to Music Periodicals Full Text',2,'',0,'https://trials.proquest.com/trials/trialSummary.action?view=subject&trialBean.token=6GVDFFAL8MDFEE3GDKXY','https://trials.proquest.com/trials/trialSummary.action?view=subject&trialBean.token=6GVDFFAL8MDFEE3GDKXY','3',2,1,0,1,48,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','This database provides indexing and abstracts for several hundred international music periodicals from over 20 countries, plus full text for more than 140 of the indexed journals. ',1413313294,1413316529,'1413313294',0,1415941200,0,0),(491,'Bloomberg BNA',1,'',0,'http://www.bna.com/bna-premier-m17179876608/','','NULL',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a Librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Bloomberg BNA is a leading source of legal, tax, regulatory, and business information for professionals, delivering expert analysis, news, practice tools, and guidance across all legal practice areas.benefits, health care, privacy &amp; data security, human resources, and environment, health &amp; safety. ',1415914243,1418312523,'1415914243',0,1418312523,0,0),(492,'Engineering Case Studies Online',1,'',7,'http://search.alexanderstreet.com/engv','http://search.alexanderstreet.com/engv','3',2,1,0,0,48,'Ask a librarian','http://answers.lib.wvu.edu/','Engineering Case Studies Online offers hundreds of hours of video and thousands of pages of text resources to meet the growing needs of engineering programs worldwide. The collection provides in-depth coverage for engineering case studies and failures, from the Titanic to the Challenger space shuttle explosion, to help students and scholars understand each case&#039;s valuable takeaways. ',1416490254,1427913969,'1416490254',0,1427913969,0,0),(493,'Learning Express Library ',1,'',0,'http://www.learningexpresshub.com/learningexpresslibrary?AuthToken=65BFD819-0275-4728-87AA-9CC9A4333686','','NULL',3,1,0,0,64,'User Guides','http://www.learningexpresshub.com/learningexpresslibrary/user-guides/full-length-video','Available on WV InfoDepot -  Test preparation (GRE, GMAT, MCAT) career planning &amp; job search, skills training for software packages and more.',1416522295,1416946561,'1416522295',0,1416946561,0,0),(495,'Dictionary of Scientific Biography -  See the Complete Dictionary of Scienctific Biography',1,'',24,'http://go.galegroup.com/ps/infomark.do?eisbn=9780684315591&userGroupName=morg77564&prodId=GVRL&action=interpret&type=aboutBook&version=1.0','','NULL',0,0,0,0,0,'','','',1421358017,1424801639,'1421358017',0,1424801639,0,0),(502,'International Code Council Online Library',1,'',0,'http://publicecodes.cyberregs.com/icod/','http://publicecodes.cyberregs.com/icod/','NULL',3,1,0,0,30,'Ask a librarian','http://westvirginia.libanswers.com/','The Interna